Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with super-resolution, which is a common problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses meta-learning to improve the performance of conventional SR networks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of AI models for super-resolution. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with neural networks and their adaptation to input images. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with improving the quality of images, which is relevant to multimedia applications.
